    public class HousePickLocationPage
extends java.lang.Object
implements IHousePoiSelect, SuperSearchResultAdapter.OnPoiItemClickListener, HPickLocationContract.View, GeocodeSearch.OnGeocodeSearchListener
    搬家业务 确认起始点Activity 说明：定位SDK type为bd09ll,百度SDK type为bd09ll 从API获取的经纬度为gcj类型，因此显示经纬度位置时需要先将gcj转为bd09ll。
